strength: Although a Super Dinosaur typically has the sameStrengthand twice theTechniqueandAttacksof its regular form, the stats of Triceratops and Super Triceratops are seemingly unrelated. name: Thunder Driver
usage: You have to win at Scissors after a win to use this Move.
effect: Throw your opponent into the air and surge yourself full of electricity, then shoot up above them and spin down, slamming into them, and drive them into the ground!
Ram and throw your opponent into the air and surge yourself full of electricity, then jump up over them and spin down, slamming into them, and drive them into the ground!

name: Mole Attack
usage: This Move activates when you win with Scissors.
effect: Somersault to burrow underground and strike your opponent from below!

Burrow underground and strike your opponent from below! The first Ankylosaurus let itself be forced underground to hide the fact it was about to use the Move, but Foolscap's simply dove underground like in the arcade game.
Effect:

name: Crystal Crusher
usage: This Move activates when you tie with any Sign after a loss triggering an elemental cataclysm.
effect: Four large crystals will rise up from the ground and float around you. Charge with them and ram into your opponent! Their defense is also lowered.

name: Gigarock Hammer
usage: This Move sometimes activates after you win with any sign.
effect: A large crystal will appear on your tail—jump up and it will grow in size several times over, then use it to smash your opponent into the ground!

name: Big Foot Assault
usage: You have to win with Scissors to use this Move.
effect: Summon Seismosaurus to crush your opponent under its feet!
Summon Seismosaurus to crush your opponent under its feet! Every normal-sized dinosaur to face this Move has been defeated in one hit.
Effect:

name: Emerald Garden
usage: This Move activates when you win with any Sign after a loss triggering an elemental cataclysm.
effect: Shoot a glowing green ball at your opponent, and have a garden spring up around them and drain their energy, sending some of it to you!
Shoot a glowing green ball at your opponent, and have a garden spring up around them and drain their energy, sending some of it to you!
Effect:

name: Thorn Whip
usage: This Move sometimes activates after an attack when you win with any move button.
effect: After your attack, a thorny vine shoots up out of the ground, whirls around, and smacks your opponent flying for extra damage!

name: Ninja Attack
usage: You have to win at Scissors to use this Move.
effect: Sprint in bursts around your opponent, leaving five duplicates of yourself surrounding them; the six of you then speed in and hit your opponent in rapid succession!

Run forward and create duplicates of yourself, all of which jump up and land around his opponent, running in a circle around them; then, the copies dash from one side to the other, slamming the opponent as they pass, the hits quickly coming faster and faster!
Effect:

name: Cyclone
usage: It triggers occasionally after a win with any Sign.
effect: Using the power of wind, you can attack through a tie! It only stays active for the round after it triggers.
A tornado surrounds you, then rush forward and ram your opponent! Ace sometimes uses it to bite his opponent's tail and swing them around, or to ram and launch them into the air.

name: Hurricane Beat
usage: You have to win at Scissors after a loss to use this Move.
effect: Send a pair of tornadoes to converge on your opponent, lifting them up into the air! Jump up and rapidly kick them in the face, then backflip and smack them away with your tail!
Send a pair of tornadoes to converge on your opponent, lifting them up into the air! Jump up and rapidly kick them in the face, then backflip and smack them away with your tail!
Effect:

name: Crimson Flame
usage: This Move activates when you win with your dinosaur's Sign.
effect: Hit your opponent with your tail, then press the two buttons shown onscreen to throw them into the air, pressing three more buttons to launch fireballs from your mouth at them! Finally, press four more buttons as they crash to stomp on them and burn them with a point-blank stream of fire from your mouth!

name: Neptune Stream
usage: This Move activates when you win with your dinosaur's sign.
effect: Smack your opponent with your tail, then press the two buttons onscreen to toss them into the air, three more buttons to shoot a beam of water from your mouth through them, and finally four more buttons for a geyser to erupt from the ground and catch them! Jump into the geyser and rise spinning to corkscrew into them!

name: Final Thunder
usage: You have to win with your dinosaur's sign to use this Move.
effect: Hit your opponent with your tail, press the two buttons onscreen to throw them into their air, then press three more buttons to charge and shoot a ball of electricity at them! Finally, press four more buttons to create an arch of electric balls over you that become spears and shoot out to skewer your opponent in midair!

Throw your opponent into the air and hit them with a bolt of lightning from your horns. An arc of electric spheres will appear over you, which will expand into stakes of electricity—shoot them at your opponent to pelt them in midair!

name: Gaia Mountain
usage: This Move activates when you win with your dinosaur's sign.
effect: Hit your opponent with your tail, press the two buttons onscreen to launch them into the air, then press three more buttons to hit a chunk of crystal at them with your tail! Finally, press four more buttons to make a large crystal spike jut out of the ground and bounce them onto a larger crystal spike jutting up that bounces them onto a giant crystal mountain that shoots out of the ground and spears them!

name: Dino Force
usage: This Move activates when you win with your dinosaur's Sign.
effect: Hit your opponent with your tail, press the two buttons shown onscreen to flip them into the air, then press the three buttons shown to call 5 Tupuxuara to fly past and hit them in midair! Finally, press the four buttons shown to call 3 Minmi to charge and ram them as they fall, after which 3 Muraenosaurus will rise from a nearby pond and shoot a trio of water bursts at them!

name: Air Raid Storm
usage: You have to win with your dinosaur's sign to use this Move.
effect: Hit your opponent with your tail, press the two buttons onscreen to throw them into the air, then press three more buttons to send a cluster of wind blades from your tail and slice them! Finally, press four more buttons and zip into midair to kick them down, then slap them with your tail, and for the finish, grab and spin them headfirst into the ground!
